key_apis_documented:
- GlideRecord: database queries and CRUD operations
- GlideSystem (gs): system utilities and logging
- GlideForm (g_form): client-side form manipulation
- GlideUser (g_user): current user information
- GlideAjax: client-to-server communication
- GlideDateTime: date/time operations
- RESTMessageV2: outbound REST calls
- RESTAPIRequest/Response: inbound REST APIs

